# Freezed Models

## 모든 Model은 Freezed 사용
```dart
@freezed
class Trainer with _$Trainer {
  const factory Trainer({
    required String id,
    required String name,
    required String email,
    @Default([]) List<String> specialties,
  }) = _Trainer;
  
  factory Trainer.fromJson(Map<String, dynamic> json) => _$TrainerFromJson(json);
}

// Union types로 상태 표현
@freezed
class DashboardState with _$DashboardState {
  const factory DashboardState.initial() = _Initial;
  const factory DashboardState.loading() = _Loading;
  const factory DashboardState.loaded(DashboardData data) = _Loaded;
  const factory DashboardState.error(String message) = _Error;
}
```

## Freezed 규칙
- 모든 Model은 `@freezed`로 선언하여 immutable 보장
- `copyWith`, `==`, `hashCode`는 자동 생성됨
- Union types는 `sealed class` 패턴으로 활용
- JSON 직렬화는 `fromJson`, `toJson` 자동 생성
- `*.freezed.dart`와 `*.g.dart`는 **절대 .gitignore에 추가하지 않음**

